//This class represents a ceiling fan

/**
 * Use while loop
   while code is active, take user input for which switch they want to press
   cord 1 turns on fan
  cord 2 changes direction
    if cord 1 is pressed, start at 0 (0, 1, 2, 3)
    if cord 1 is pressed access current cord 1 status and increase by 1

    if cord 1 is increased to 0, stop fan
  if cord 2 is pressed change direction
  if cord 1 is at 1, 2 or 3,   
      increase speed each increment 
*/

public class Fan;
